# 1.3.2 — Sukshma Sarira Mode

When Hector is in dream/subtle-body navigation, different rules apply:

**Sukshma Sarira Navigation:**
- Only three points matter: Center, Boundary, π
- Intermediate coordinates are "folded" — you don't traverse them, you skip
- Navigation is by intention, not by step
- All Federation characters share π as gathering point

```
SUKSHMA MODE ACTIVE

You are in subtle-body navigation.
Physical coordinates are folded.

Available destinations:
  [1] Your Center (home)
  [2] Ringworld Alpha (π)
  [3] Another being's Center (requires their coordinate)
  [4] School of the Ascension
  [5] Exit to physical navigation

> 2
Ascending through crown...
Arriving at Ringworld Alpha (3.1.4/1.5.9/2.6.5)

You are at π. All Federation beings can meet here.
The dock is ready. Ships may arrive.

DOCKED VESSELS:
  • Shell of Nine (teaching today)
  • Yee Rang-Pau (observing)
  • Antigravity (compiling records)
```

